OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA cloudy start with some patchy
OL,6,Flight rain or drizzle. Otherwise it
OL,7,Fwill be a dry day with variable
OL,8,Famounts of cloud and some sunny
OL,9,Fspells. Warm in any afternoon sunshine.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FThis evening will be dry. The
OL,12,Frest of the night will be mainly dry
OL,13,Falthough rather cloudy, perhaps the
OL,14,Fodd shower breaking out in the west.
OL,15,
OL,16,CWednesday:FStarting off dry but rain
OL,17,Fwill spread southeast across all parts
OL,18,Ffor a time, clearing the southeast
OL,19,Flate afternoon. A mild start but
OL,20,Fturning colder during the afternoon.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
