OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:FDry
OL,6,Ffor most of Thursday but patchy rain
OL,7,Fpossible in the evening. Unsettled
OL,8,Fwith showers or longer spells of rain
OL,9,Fon Friday and Saturday.
